fields.name: Box of Eight Traditional Welsh Cakes
fields.description: Made to a traditional recipe passed down through several generations. Made with sultanas and a small pinch of nutmeg, these are fresh from the bakestone.

fields.name: Box of Eight Cinnamon Welsh Cakes
fields.description: Add some spice to your life! Made to a traditional recipe including sultanas.

fields.name: Box of Eight Cranberry and White Chocolate Welshcakes
fields.description: The tried-and-tested of cranberry and sweet white chocolate comes to our welsh cakes! This was a voted flavour that was so popular, it is now one of our staple picks.

fields.name: Box of Eight Lemon and Poppyseed Welshcakes
fields.description: One of our regular's daughters suggested this recipe! Buy it while you can! Zesty lemon complements this delicious treat!

fields.name: Box of Eight Coconut Welshcakes
fields.description: A tropical twist. Combines well with jam!

fields.name: Box of Eight Gluten Free Welshcakes
fields.description: Self-raising flour and gluten-free goodness, made with sultanas and a pinch of nutmeg!

fields.name: Box of Eight Vegan Welshcakes
fields.description: Made with our new vegan recipe, this is a dairy-free option whether you've been vegan for a while or as soon as January (or Veganuary)!

fields.name: Welshcake Lovers Hamper
fields.description: A gift box of our three classic box sets: Eight each of our Traditional, Milk Chocolate and Cinnamon welsh cakes, as well as a gift card from us.

fields.name: Tea Lovers Hamper
fields.description: Two boxes of our Traditional Welsh Cakes, along with a box of Cariad tea bags and a Sarah Bunton hot chocolate stirrer. The perfect care package to send to someone at home or further away!

fields.name: Welshcake Tin
fields.description: Store your welshcakes in a tin! This is the perfect gift for someone with a Welsh sweet tooth!

fields.name: Corgi Welshcake Cutter
fields.description: This is a set of 3 x 4 inch cutters perfect for making themed biscuits or welsh cakes!

fields.name: Dragon Welshcake Cutter
fields.description: This is a set of 3 x 4 inch cutters perfect for making themed biscuits or welsh cakes!

fields.name: Box of Eight Milk Chocolate Welshcakes
fields.description: Milk chocolate replaces sultanas for your inner chocoholic - or any chocoholics you know!
